    <p>The Lexus IS (right) has un­der­gone a makeover for next year, with bolder body mould­ings, restyled lights back and front and a host of ad­di­tional ameni­ties.</p>
    <p>These in­clude a 10.3-inch in­fo­tain­ment touch­screen sys­tem with Ap­ple and An­droid com­pat­i­bil­ity, adap­tive cruise con­trol and park­ing as­sist.</p>
    <p>Driv­ing and safety fea­tures such as lane-trac­ing as­sist and pre­c­ol­li­sion steer­ing as­sist are also avail­able.</p>
    <p>The car was un­veiled here on Thurs­day.</p>


